snippet.title: OXENFREE: Official Teaser #2
snippet.description: OXENFREE is coming in January 2016, making it's console debut on Xbox One!  Night School Studio's OXENFREE is a supernatural teen thriller about a group of friends who unwittingly open a ghostly rift. Players control Alex, who brings her new stepbrother Jonas to an overnight party gone wrong off the coast of their hometown.
